    "en": {
      "title": "Colombo Fort violence incident: Three bailed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three persons including Rathindu Senaratne and Lahiru Weerasekhara, who were remanded in connection with the violent incidents in Colombo Fort and Talangama areas, have been released on bail.",
        "After the said three persons were produced in the Colombo Fort Magistrate's Court this morning (1), Fort Magistrate Dilina Gamage ordered them to be released on personal bail of 5 lakh rupees each. (a)"
      ],
